@media (max-width : 540px) {
  .tingle-modal {
    top: 0px;
    display: block;
    padding-top: 60px;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .tingle-modal-box {
    width: auto;
    border-radius: 0;
  }

  .tingle-modal-box__content {
    overflow-y: scroll;
  }

  .tingle-modal--noClose {
    top: 0;
  }

  .tingle-modal--noOverlayClose {
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .tingle-modal-box__footer .tingle-btn {
    display: block;
    float: none;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    width: 100%;
  }

  .tingle-modal__close {
    top: 0;
    right: 0;
    left: 0;
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    height: 60px;
    border: none;
    background-color: #2c3e50;
    box-shadow: none;
    color: #fff;
  }

  .tingle-modal__closeLabel {
    display: inline-block;
    vertical-align: middle;
    font-size: 1.6rem;
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Roboto", "Oxygen", "Ubuntu", "Cantarell", "Fira Sans", "Droid Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
  }

  .tingle-modal__closeIcon {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-right: .8rem;
    width: 1.6rem;
    vertical-align: middle;
    font-size: 0;
  }
}

    opacity: 0;
    transform: scale(.9);
  }

    opacity: 1;
    transform: scale(1);
  }

    width: auto;
    border-radius: 0;

/* modal
-------------------------------------------------------------- */

.tingle-modal--noOverlayClose {
  cursor: default;
}

.tingle-modal--noClose .tingle-modal__close {
  display: none;
}

.tingle-modal__close {
  position: fixed;
  top: 2.5rem;
  right: 2.5rem;
  z-index: 1000;
  padding: 0;
  width: 2rem;
  height: 2rem;
  border: none;
  background-color: transparent;
  color: #fff;
  cursor: pointer;
}

  fill: currentColor;
}

.tingle-modal__closeLabel {
  display: none;
}

.tingle-modal__close:hover {
  color: #fff;
}

.tingle-modal-box {
  position: relative;
  flex-shrink: 0;
  margin-top: auto;
  margin-bottom: auto;
  width: 60%;
  border-radius: 4px;
  background: #fff;
  opacity: 1;
  cursor: auto;
  will-change: transform, opacity;
}

.tingle-modal-box__content {
  padding: 3rem 3rem;
}

.tingle-modal-box__footer {
  padding: 1.5rem 2rem;
  width: auto;

  border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;
  background-color: #f5f5f5;
  cursor: auto;
}

  clear: both;
  content: "";
}

.tingle-modal-box__footer--sticky {
  position: fixed;
  bottom: -200px; /* TODO : find a better way */

  opacity: 1;
  transition: bottom .3s ease-in-out .3s;
}

/* state
-------------------------------------------------------------- */

  position: fixed;
  right: 0;
  left: 0;
  overflow: hidden;
}

  bottom: 0;
}

.tingle-modal--visible {
  visibility: visible;
  opacity: 1;
}

  animation: scale .2s cubic-bezier(.68, -.55, .265, 1.55) forwards;
}

.tingle-modal--overflow {
  overflow-y: scroll;
  padding-top: 8vh;
}

    function prepaidEnscroll_waitlist() {
        if (typeof (isFromipadApp) != "undefined" && !iPadAndroid && !iMacSafari && $('.waitlistnewbody').data("enscroll") == undefined) {
            $(".waitlistnewbody").enscroll({
                addPaddingToPane: false,
                horizontalScrolling: false,
                horizontalTrackClass: 'horizontal-track2',
                horizontalHandleClass: 'horizontal-handle2',
                showOnHover: false,
                verticalTrackClass: 'track3',
                scrollIncrement: 40,
                verticalHandleClass: 'handle3',
                cornerClass: 'corner2'
            });
        }

    }

<script>    
    function callButtonpayrollhistory() {
        alert('Some error occurred. please try again!!');
    }
    function downloadPaystubPDFFile() {
        var base64Pdf = document.getElementById('hdnBase64DataPdf').value;
        if (base64Pdf != undefined && base64Pdf != null && base64Pdf != "") {
            if (isBase64Valid(base64Pdf)) {
                var base64String = "data:application/pdf;charset=utf-8;base64," + base64Pdf;
                var message = '{"message": "","messageType": 0,"screenTitle":"","screenType": 0,"navType": 0,"action": "81|~|' + base64String + '" }';
                console.log(message);
                CallbackforPayrollHistory(message);
            }
        }
        return false;
    }
    function isBase64Valid(base64String) {
        try {
            atob(base64String);
            return true;
        } catch (e) {
            return false;
        }
    }
    function CallbackforPayrollHistory(message) {
        var objData = '5006||~||' + message;
        if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("safari") < 0 && (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("iphone") > -1 || navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("ipad") > -1)) {
            window.location = "js-call:myObjectiveCFunction:" + objData;
        }
        else if (navigator.userAgent.toLowerCase().indexOf("android") > -1) {
            if (!(window.JSInterface == undefined)) {
                window.JSInterface.CallWSMethod(objData);
            }
        }
        else {
            if (!(window.JSInterface == undefined)) {
                window.JSInterface.CallWSMethod(objData);
            }
        }
    }
</script>

<script type="text/javascript">
    dInfoValue = "";
    var IsBlockUserByPass = 'True'.toLowerCase() == 'true' ? true : false;
    if (navigator.userAgent != null && navigator.userAgent.indexOf("com.vagaro.customerios") > -1) { } else {
        if (typeof (fpPromise) == 'undefined') {
            var fpEndPoint = "https://fp.vagaro.com";
            var isLWSite = JSON.parse('True'.toLowerCase());
            if (isLWSite == false) {
                fpEndPoint = "https://fp.bookitall.com";
            }
            const fpPromise = new Promise((resolve, reject) => {
                const script = document.createElement('script');
                script.onload = resolve;
                script.onerror = reject;
                script.async = true;
                script.src = 'https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/'
                    + '@fingerprintjs/fingerprintjs-pro@3/dist/fp.min.js';
                document.head.appendChild(script);
            })
                .then(() => FingerprintJS.load({ token: document.getElementById('hdnFingurePrintJSToken').value, endpoint: fpEndPoint }));




            function kickOff(p) {
                //if (IsBlockUserByPass == true) {
                    //login(p, "");
                   // return;
                //}

                var vid = "";
                try {
                    if (typeof localStorage === 'object') {
                        vid = localStorage.getItem("_vid_fp");
                        if (vid == null) {
                            vid = "";
                        }

                    }
                } catch (e) {

                }
                if (typeof (fpPromise) != 'undefined' && (typeof (vid) == 'undefined' || vid == null || vid == "" || vid == "null" || vid == "n/a" || vid == "undefined")) {
                    fpPromise
                        .then(fp => fp.get())
                        .then(result => {
                            try {
                                const visitorId = result.visitorId
                                vid = visitorId;
                                if (typeof (vid) == 'undefined' || vid == "" || vid == null || vid == "null" || vid == "n/a" || vid == "undefined") {
                                    SaveAILog(result);
                                    vid = "";
                                }
                            } catch (e) {
                                login(p, "");
                                SaveAILog(result);
                            }
                        })
                        .then(function () {
                            dInfoValue = vid;
                            fpDeviceId = vid;
                            try {
                                if (typeof localStorage === 'object' && vid != "") {
                                    localStorage.setItem("_vid_fp", vid);
                                }
                            } catch (e) {

                            }
                            login(p, vid);
                        })
                        .catch(error => {
                            login(p, "");
                            SaveAILog(error);
                        })
                } else {
                    dInfoValue = vid;
                    fpDeviceId = vid;
                    login(p, vid);
                }
            }
            function kickOffSignup() {
                if (IsBlockUserByPass == true) {
                    return;
                }

                var vid = "";
                try {
                    if (typeof localStorage === 'object') {
                        vid = localStorage.getItem("_vid_fp");
                    }
                } catch (e) {

                }
                if (typeof (fpPromise) != 'undefined' && (typeof (vid) == 'undefined' || vid == null || vid == "" || vid == "null" || vid == "n/a" || vid == "undefined")) {
                    fpPromise
                        .then(fp => fp.get())
                        .then(result => {
                            const visitorId = result.visitorId
                            vid = visitorId;
                            if (typeof (vid) == 'undefined' || vid == "" || vid == null || vid == "null" || vid == "n/a" || vid == "undefined") {
                                SaveAILog(result);
                                vid = "";
                            }
                        })
                        .then(function () {
                            dInfoValue = vid;
                            fpDeviceId = vid;
                            try {
                                if (typeof localStorage === 'object' && vid != "") {
                                    localStorage.setItem("_vid_fp", vid);
                                }
                            }
                            catch (e) {

                            }
                        })
                        .catch(error => {
                            SaveAILog(error);
                            dInfoValue = "";
                            fpDeviceId = "";
                        })
                }
                else {
                    dInfoValue = vid;
                    fpDeviceId = vid;
                }
            }
            function login(p, vid) {
                p += ', "vid" : "' + vid + '"';
                if (typeof currentPage != "undefined" && currentPage != null && currentPage != '' && currentPage == "LoginASPX") {
                    vid = "";
                    p += ', "fpID" : "' + vid + '"';
                }
                else {
                    p += ', "fpID" : "' + vid + '"';
                }
                if ((typeof _common != "undefined" && typeof _common.IsCookieLessWidget != "undefined" && _common.IsCookieLessWidget())) {
                    p += ', "isFromCookieLessWidget" : true';
                }
                else {
                    p += ', "isFromCookieLessWidget" : false';
                }
                p += ', "ssoId" : ""';
                p += ', "acctkn" : ""';
                CallWebServicehed('MySampleService.asmx/SignIn', p, CallSuccessLoginCtrl, CallFailed);
            }
            function SaveAILog(result) {
                try {
                    var objReq = {
                        jsonData: JSON.stringify(result),
                        functionName: "Login Fingure PrintID Check",
                        lBusinessID: 11111,
                    };

                    var AjaxPostcall = new vagaro.ajax();
                    AjaxPostcall.datamodel.Token = "addbusiness/signupbusinessailog";
                    AjaxPostcall.datamodel.data = objReq;
                    AjaxPostcall.datamodel.IsNewVagaroAPI = true;
                    AjaxPostcall.datamodel.callback = function () { };
                    AjaxPostcall.datamodel.Error = function () { };
                    AjaxPostcall.Post();
                } catch (e) {
                }
            }

            function GetVidForBusinessMultiSignup() {
                var vid = "";
                try {
                    if (typeof localStorage === 'object') {
                        vid = localStorage.getItem("_vid_fp");
                        if (vid == null) {
                            vid = "";
                        }
                    }
                }
                catch (e) {

                }
                if (typeof (fpPromise) != 'undefined' && (typeof (vid) == 'undefined' || vid == null || vid == "" || vid == "null" || vid == "n/a" || vid == "undefined")) {
                    fpPromise
                        .then(fp => fp.get())
                        .then(result => {
                            try {
                                const visitorId = result.visitorId
                                vid = visitorId;
                                if (typeof (vid) == 'undefined' || vid == "" || vid == null || vid == "null" || vid == "n/a" || vid == "undefined") {
                                    vid = "";
                                }
                            } catch (e) {
                            }
                        })
                        .then(function () {
                            $("#hdnVId").val(vid);
                            try {
                            if (typeof localStorage === 'object' && vid != "") {
                                localStorage.setItem("_vid_fp", vid);
                                }
                            }
                            catch (e) {

                            }
                        })
                        .catch(error => {
                        })
                }
                else {
                    $("#hdnVId").val(vid);
                }
            }
        }
    }

        function botCheck() {
            try {
                var botPattern = "(googlebot\/|Googlebot-Mobile|Googlebot-Image|Google favicon|Mediapartners-Google|bingbot|slurp|java|wget|curl|Commons-HttpClient|Python-urllib|libwww|httpunit|nutch|phpcrawl|msnbot|jyxobot|FAST-WebCrawler|FAST Enterprise Crawler|biglotron|teoma|convera|seekbot|gigablast|exabot|ngbot|ia_archiver|GingerCrawler|webmon |httrack|webcrawler|grub.org|UsineNouvelleCrawler|antibot|netresearchserver|speedy|fluffy|bibnum.bnf|findlink|msrbot|panscient|yacybot|AISearchBot|IOI|ips-agent|tagoobot|MJ12bot|dotbot|woriobot|yanga|buzzbot|mlbot|yandexbot|purebot|Linguee Bot|Voyager|CyberPatrol|voilabot|baiduspider|citeseerxbot|spbot|twengabot|postrank|turnitinbot|scribdbot|page2rss|sitebot|linkdex|Adidxbot|blekkobot|ezooms|dotbot|Mail.RU_Bot|discobot|heritrix|findthatfile|europarchive.org|NerdByNature.Bot|sistrix crawler|ahrefsbot|Aboundex|domaincrawler|wbsearchbot|summify|ccbot|edisterbot|seznambot|ec2linkfinder|gslfbot|aihitbot|intelium_bot|facebookexternalhit|yeti|RetrevoPageAnalyzer|lb-spider|sogou|lssbot|careerbot|wotbox|wocbot|ichiro|DuckDuckBot|lssrocketcrawler|drupact|webcompanycrawler|acoonbot|openindexspider|gnam gnam spider|web-archive-net.com.bot|backlinkcrawler|coccoc|integromedb|content crawler spider|toplistbot|seokicks-robot|it2media-domain-crawler|ip-web-crawler.com|siteexplorer.info|elisabot|proximic|changedetection|blexbot|arabot|WeSEE:Search|niki-bot|CrystalSemanticsBot|rogerbot|360Spider|psbot|InterfaxScanBot|Lipperhey SEO Service|CC Metadata Scaper|g00g1e.net|GrapeshotCrawler|urlappendbot|brainobot|fr-crawler|binlar|SimpleCrawler|Livelapbot|Twitterbot|cXensebot|smtbot|bnf.fr_bot|A6-Indexer|ADmantX|Facebot|Twitterbot|OrangeBot|memorybot|AdvBot|MegaIndex|SemanticScholarBot|ltx71|nerdybot|xovibot|BUbiNG|Qwantify|archive.org_bot|Applebot|TweetmemeBot|crawler4j|findxbot|SemrushBot|yoozBot|lipperhey|y!j-asr|Domain Re-Animator Bot|AddThis)";
                var re = new RegExp(botPattern, 'i');
                var userAgent = navigator.userAgent;
                if (re.test(userAgent)) {
                    return true;
                } else {
                    return false;
                }
            } catch (e) {
                return false;
            }
        }

        function changeFavicon(src) {
            $('link[rel="shortcut icon"]').attr('href', src)
            $('link[rel="apple-touch-icon"]').each(function (index) {
                $(this).attr('href', src);
            });
            $('link[rel="icon"]').each(function (index) {
                $(this).attr('href', src);
            });
        }

        //Add page histoy for windows app
        function addPageHistoryWinApp(basePage, tabName, businessName) {
            if (isWindowsApp) {
                window.external.notify("addhistorystate|" + basePage + "|" + (tabName != "/" ? tabName : "") + "|" + (typeof (businessName) != 'undefined' && businessName != null ? businessName : ""));
            }
        }

        //Code for windows app, do not delete this function
        function loadTabFromWinApp(basePage, tabName, businessName) {
            if (basePage == BasePage) {
                if (basePage.toLowerCase() == "home" || basePage.toLowerCase() == "dailydeal") {
                    if (tabName.indexOf(",") > -1) {
                        var arr = tabName.split(",");
                        if (arr.length == 3) {
                            DailyDealsDetail(arr[0], arr[1], arr[2]);
                        }
                    }
                    else {
                        _common.loadSectionsFromMobile(tabName);
                    }
                }
                else if (basePage.toLowerCase() == "detail") {
                    if (tabName == "" || tabName == "about") {
                        _shopdetail.backpage();
                    }
                    else {
                        _shopdetail.LoadTabs(tabName);
                    }
                }
                else if (basePage.toLowerCase() == "myaccount") {
                    _myAccount.loadMyAccountData(tabName, 0);
                }
            }
            else {
                var strUrl = "";
                if (basePage.toLowerCase() == "home" || basePage.toLowerCase() == "dailydeal") {
                    if (tabName.indexOf(",") > -1) {
                        var arr = tabName.split(",");
                        if (arr.length == 3) {
                            strUrl = arr[2];
                        }
                    }
                    else {
                        strUrl = tabName == "/" ? "" : tabName;
                    }
                }
                else if (basePage.toLowerCase() == "detail") {
                    strUrl = businessName + "/" + (tabName == "/" ? "" : tabName);
                }
                else if (basePage.toLowerCase() == "myaccount") {
                    strUrl = basePage + "/" + (tabName == "/" ? "" : tabName);
                }

                location.href = location.protocol + '//' + location.host + "/" + strUrl;
            }
        }

        if (typeof (AddThisPadding) != "undefined")
            AddThisPadding();
        if (typeof (lazyloadDeal) != "undefined")
            lazyloadDeal();
    </script>

                    _common.ScrollToToZero();
                }

                // set cookie with domain , amit t on 22-mar-19
                //$.cookie('cmsmaster', 'public', { path: '/' });
                cookieManager.setCookie('cmsmaster', 'public', '', cookieManager.defaultPath, cookieManager.defaultDomain, true);

                tabSegment = 'profile';
                if (window.location.hash != '') {
                    try {
                        tabSegment = window.location.hash.substr(1);
                    } catch (ex) { }
                }
                $("img.lazy").lazyload({ effect: "fadeIn" });

                if (typeof vgAppicationType == 'undefined' || vgAppicationType != 1) {
                    mobileMenu();
                }
                LoadDataByPage(tabSegment);
                setTimeout(function () { ignoreHistory_IOS = false; }, 2500);

                isDoingUpload = 'false';
                if (isDoingUpload == 'true') {
                    $("#mobilemenutoggle").attr('onclick', 'javascript:void(0);');
                    $(".dropdown-arrow").hide();
                }
            }(jQuery, window, document));
        }

        function isSearchLocationVisible() {
            if ($('#txtLocationSearch').is(':visible') == true || $('#txtBusinessLocationSearch').is(':visible')) {
                return true;
            }
            return false;
        }

        function GetLatLong() {
            try {
                clearInterval(GoogleApiTimeInterval);               
                CountryID = localStorage.getItem('SalesCountryId');
                if (CountryID != null && CountryID != undefined && CountryID > 0) {
                    SetCountry(CountryID);
                }
                else if (botCheck() || (typeof vgAppicationType != 'undefined' && vgAppicationType == 1)) {
                    SetCountry(1);
                }
                else {
                    if (countryid != undefined && countryid != null) {
                        SetCountry(countryid)
                    }
                    else {
                        SetCountry(1);
                    }
                }
            } catch (e) {
            }

        }

        function GetCountry(lat, lon) {            
            try {
                clearInterval(GoogleApiTimeInterval);
                CountryID = localStorage.getItem('SalesCountryId');
                if (CountryID != null && CountryID != undefined  && CountryID > 0)
                {
                    SetCountry(CountryID);
                }
                else if (botCheck() || (typeof vgAppicationType != 'undefined' && vgAppicationType == 1)) {
                    SetCountry(1);
                }                
                else {
                    if (countryid != undefined && countryid != null) {
                        SetCountry(countryid);
                    }
                    //var vgPosition = new vagaro.ajax();
                    //vgPosition.datamodel.Token = 'GetCurrentLocation';
                    //vgPosition.datamodel.data = [lat, lon, 25];
                    //vgPosition.datamodel.callback = function (result) {
                    //    if (result != null) {
                    //        CountryID = result.countryID;
                    //        SetCountry(CountryID);

                    //    }
                    //}
                    //vgPosition.datamodel.Error = function (e) {
                    //}
                    //vgPosition.Post();
                }
            } catch (e) {
            }

        }

        function SetCountry(CountryID) {
            try {
                var today = new Date();
                //localStorage.setItem('SalesCountryId', CountryID);
                //localStorage.setItem('SalesCountryExpiry', today);
                if (CountryID != null) {
                    $('a[href*="https://www.vagaro.com/pro"],a[href*="https://www.vagaro.com/en-"]').each(function (url) {
                        if (CountryID == 2) {
                            this.href = this.href.replace('/pro', '/en-gb/pro');
                        }
                        else if (CountryID == 3) {
                            this.href = this.href.replace('/pro', '/en-ca/pro');
                        }
                        else if (CountryID == 4) {
                            this.href = this.href.replace('/pro', '/en-au/pro');
                        }
                    });
                }
            } catch (e) {
            }

        }

        function InitializeTimer() {
            try {
               
            var CountryID = localStorage.getItem('SalesCountryId')
            if (CountryID != null) {
                SetCountry(CountryID);
                clearInterval(GoogleApiTimeInterval);
                return;
            }
            if (isGetLocation) {
                SetCountry(CountryID);
                clearInterval(GoogleApiTimeInterval);
            }
            else {
                GetLatLong();
            }
            } catch (e) {
                clearInterval(GoogleApiTimeInterval);
            }
        }

        function LoadDataByPage(tabSegment) {
            if ((BasePage == "Home" || isSearchLocationVisible() == true) && typeof isFirstTimeCall != "undefined" && isFirstTimeCall.toLowerCase() == 'true') {
                if (typeof vgAppicationType != 'undefined' && vgAppicationType == 1) {
                    CallbackforMobileApp(0, 0, '', '', 0, 27);
                }
                else {
                    findCurrentLocation(null, null, null, null, 'loaddatabypage', tabSegment);
                }
            }
            /*Added By Nirav Savariya for Branded App Project on 19-08-2019*/
            else if (BasePage == "BrandedAppChooseBusiness" && typeof vgAppicationType != 'undefined' && vgAppicationType == 1) {
                CallbackforMobileApp(0, 0, '', '', 0, 27);
            }
            else {
                GetLatLong()                
            }

            if (typeof (_shopdetail.isCustomWebsite) == "undefined" || _shopdetail.isCustomWebsite != "true") {
                if (typeof refUrl != 'undefined' && refUrl.length > 0
                    && (decodeURIComponent(refUrl).toLowerCase().indexOf("/listings/") > 0
                        || encodeURIComponent(decodeURIComponent(refUrl)).toLowerCase().indexOf('https%3a%2f%2fwww.vagaro.com%2fmyaccount%2fprofile') != -1) //decoded and Encoded URL Again to resolve XSS (Cross Site Scripting) attack.
                    && tabSegment == "about"
                ) {
                    referrer = 'false';
                }
                flagBackButton = $("#mobile-check").is(":visible") && (referrer == 'true' || history.state != null) && tabSegment != "home" && tabSegment != "/" && tabSegment != "";
                if (flagBackButton) {
                    $("#mobileBack").show();
                    $("#custmobileBack").hide();
                }
            }
            if (BasePage == "Home") {
                clearCookie("newdesign");
                clearCookie("PreviewId");
                clearCookie("customedesign");
                // Nehal : 26/07/2019 - Below cookie is used in Branded App
                clearCookie("CustomizableBusinessID"); //changed by amit t on 18-jan-19 , declare cookie name as global and remove static text , use "s_" for staging
                _common.CheckPromoBusinessID();
                _common.showHideBackandCart(false);
                var iscookie = SetProximityVariables(tabSegment);
                var ck = getCookie(ProximityCookieName);

                if (iscookie) {

                    if (_common.hasLatLongCookie() == false) {
                        _common.SetDefaultLocation(tabSegment, ck);
                    }
                    else {
                        setDropDown();
                        loadData(tabSegment, true);
                        _common.setGeoLocationMarker(tabSegment);
                    }
                }
                $(".cancel-select-service").on("touchstart click", function (e) {
                    e.preventDefault();
                    e.stopPropagation();

                    if (typeof isFilterScreen != 'undefined' && isFilterScreen) {
                        $("#select2-drop-mask").click();
                        $("#txtSearchServiceMain").select2("close");
                    }
                    else if (parseInt($("#btnBackHomeSearch:visible").data("iscustomerappsearch")) == 1) {
                        $(this).parent().find(".select2-input").blur();
                        $("#btnBackHomeSearch:visible").click();
                    }
                    else {
                        $("#select2-drop-mask").click();
                    }
                    $("html, body").removeClass('searchaddservclass');
                });
            }
            else if (BasePage == "MyAccount") {
                if (typeof vgAppicationType != 'undefined' && vgAppicationType == 1) {
                    if (typeof (tabSegment) != undefined && tabSegment.toLowerCase() != "appointments") {
                        $("#mobileBack").hide();
                        $("#custmobileBack").show();
                    }

                    $(".profile-footer-btns").each(function () {
                        if ($(this).children().length > 1) {
                            $(this).find("#btnCancel").hide();
                        }
                        else {
                            $(this).hide();
                        }
                    });
                }

                _myAccount.initializeMyaccount('profile');
                _common.showHideBackandCart(false);
                SetProximityVariables();
                if (false == ((_shopdetail.isCustomWebsite != undefined && _shopdetail.isCustomWebsite == "true") || (_shopdetail.isFacebook != undefined && _shopdetail.isFacebook == "true") || (_shopdetail.isWidget != undefined && _shopdetail.isWidget == "true"))) {
                    setDropDown();
                }
            }
            else if (BasePage == "Detail") {
                _shopdetail.LoadTabs(tabSegment);
                SetProximityVariables();

                if (typeof vgAppicationType == 'undefined' || vgAppicationType != 1) {
                    if (false == ((_shopdetail.isCustomWebsite != undefined && _shopdetail.isCustomWebsite == "true") || (_shopdetail.isFacebook != undefined && _shopdetail.isFacebook == "true") || (_shopdetail.isWidget != undefined && _shopdetail.isWidget == "true"))) {
                        setDropDown();
                    }
                }

                //$(".cancel-select-service").on("touchstart click", function (e) {
                //    e.preventDefault();
                //    e.stopPropagation();
                //    $("#select2-drop-mask").click();
                //});
            }
            else {
                SetProximityVariables();
                setDropDown();
                _common.setviewport();
            }

            //Added by Rakesh Raval for VPL invite 
            if (typeof refUrl != 'undefined' && refUrl.length > 0 && decodeURIComponent(refUrl).toLowerCase().indexOf("/paylatersignup/") > 0) {
                $('.login-backbtn').attr("onclick", "Javascript:BackToVPLInvite('" + refUrl + "'); ");
            }
        }

        //Added by Rakesh Raval for VPL invite 
        function BackToVPLInvite(url) {
            window.location.href = url;
        }

        if (IsAjaxEnabled == 'True') {
            (function (d) {
                var f = d.getElementsByTagName('SCRIPT')[0], p = d.createElement('SCRIPT');
                p.type = 'text/javascript';
                p.async = true;
                p.src = 'https://assets.pinterest.com/js/pinit.js';
                f.parentNode.insertBefore(p, f);
            }(document));
        }

        var userAgent = (navigator.userAgent || navigator.vendor || window.opera).toLowerCase();
        var iAppleDevice = userAgent.match(/ipad/i) || userAgent.match(/iphone/i) || userAgent.match(/itouch/i) || userAgent.match(/android/i) || userAgent.match(/mac/i) || false;
        if (iAppleDevice) {
            $('body').addClass('iAppleDevice')
        }

        

        /*SEO: Referral url changes Start*/
        window.onmessage = function (e) {

            var salespage = "https://www.vagaro.com/pro";

            if (document.referrer.indexOf(salespage) > 0) {
                return;
            }
            try {
                var payload = JSON.parse(e.data);
                if (payload != undefined && payload != null && payload.key != undefined && payload.data != undefined) {
                    localStorage.setItem(payload.key, JSON.stringify(payload.data));
                }
            } catch (e) {
                //console.log(e.message);
            }
        };

        //Need to confirm(some other domain to direct landing vagaro.com domain)
        window.onload = function () {
            setTimeout(postMessagetoWindow, 1);
            /* https://vagaro.zendesk.com/agent/tickets/308557
           window.onload was not called second time,So banner was not set in detai page.
        */
            if (typeof (_shopdetail) != "undefined" && typeof (_shopdetail.setCustomWebBanner) === "function") {
                _shopdetail.setCustomWebBanner();
            }
        };

        function postMessagetoWindow() {
            var referrerUrl = document.referrer;
            //vagaro.com
            //sales.vagaro.com
            var livevagaro = "vagaro.com";
            if (window.location.href.toLowerCase().indexOf("gclid=") > -1) {
                referrerUrl = "google ads";
            }
            else if (window.location.href.toLowerCase().indexOf("srcuri=vagarofbads") > -1) {
                referrerUrl = "facebook ads";
            }

            if (referrerUrl.indexOf(livevagaro) > -1 || referrerUrl.indexOf("sales.vagaro.com") > -1) {
                return;
            }
            else if (window.location.href.indexOf(livevagaro) > -1 && referrerUrl != null && referrerUrl != undefined && referrerUrl != '') {
                try {
                    localStorage.setItem("urlReferrer", referrerUrl);

                } catch (e) {
                    // console.log(e.message);
                }
            }
        }

        
        /*SEO: Referral url changes End*/

        //$(document).ajaxError(function (event, request, settings) {
        //    //if (settings.url.indexOf('HelloWorld') > 0) {
        //    if (request.status == 403 || request.status == 500)
        //        location.reload(true);
        //    //}
        //});
        function GetSalesURL(URLPath, IsNewTab) {
            URLPath = (typeof URLPath != "undefined" && URLPath != null) ? URLPath : "";
            var redirectURL = "https://www.vagaro.com/pro/" + URLPath;
            var ProximityState = getCookie('proximitystate_v3');
            var CountryId = (typeof ProximityState != "undefined" && ProximityState != null && typeof ProximityState.countryid != "undefined" && ProximityState.countryid != null) ? parseInt(ProximityState.countryid) : 1;
            if (CountryId == 2) {
                redirectURL = "https://www.vagaro.com/en-gb/pro/" + URLPath;
            }
            else if (CountryId == 3) {
                redirectURL = "https://www.vagaro.com/en-ca/pro/" + URLPath;
            }
            else if (CountryId == 4) {
                redirectURL = "https://www.vagaro.com/en-au/pro/" + URLPath;
            }
            if (IsNewTab) {

                $("#SalesLink").attr("href", redirectURL);
                var el = document.getElementById('SalesLink');
                el.click();
            } else {
                window.location.href = redirectURL;
            }

            return false;
        }


    </script>

<script type="text/javascript">
    setTimeout(function () {
        if (typeof (isWindowsApp) != "undefined" && isWindowsApp) {
            fbLoaderCompleted();
        }
    }, 3000);
    
    function fbLoaderCompleted() {
        if ($("#divFacebookLoader").length > 0 && $("#divGoogleLoader").length > 0) {  //Added by Abdeli Dhankot to check Branded APP Rejection change on 08/10/2020
            if (typeof isBrandedAppForApproval != "undefined" && isBrandedAppForApproval == true) {
                $("#aFBSignup").hide();
            }
            else {
                $("#divFacebookLoader").closest('.facebook-btn').attr("style", "");
            }
            if ($("#aFBSignup").length > 0)
                $("#aFBSignup").attr("onclick", "javascript:return frmsignupnew.login(3);");
            if ($("#aFBLogin").length > 0)
                $("#aFBLogin").attr("onclick", "javascript:return frmlogin.login(3);");

            $("#divFacebookLoader").hide();
            if (typeof (isWidget) !== "undefined" && isWidget == 'true' && typeof (CheckWidgetForGoogle) != "undefined" && CheckWidgetForGoogle == 'True') {
                $('#aGoogleSignup').hide();
                $("#signupheaderpart").hide();
                $("#divNewToVagaro").hide();
            }
            else {
                if (typeof isBrandedAppForApproval != "undefined" && isBrandedAppForApproval == true) { 
                    $('#aGoogleSignup').hide();
                } else {
                    $('#aGoogleSignup').show();
                    $("#divGoogleLoader").closest('.facebook-btn').attr("style", "");
                }
            }
            if ($("#aGoogleSignUp").length > 0)
                $("#aGoogleSignUp").attr("onclick", "javascript:return frmsignupnew.login(2);");
            if ($("#aGoogleLogin").length > 0)
                $("#aGoogleLogin").attr("onclick", "javascript:return frmlogin.login(2);");

            $("#divGoogleLoader").hide();
        }
    }

    (function (w, d) {

        if ('function' !== typeof w.$FacebookLoader) {
            w.$FacebookLoader = function (callback, options) {
                if (typeof (IsBrandedApp) != "undefined" && IsBrandedApp != undefined && IsBrandedApp != null && IsBrandedApp == true) {
                }
                else if (typeof (IsNewVersionCustomerAppForFbGoogleLogin) != "undefined" && IsNewVersionCustomerAppForFbGoogleLogin != undefined && IsNewVersionCustomerAppForFbGoogleLogin !== "" && IsNewVersionCustomerAppForFbGoogleLogin != null && IsNewVersionCustomerAppForFbGoogleLogin == true) {
                }
                else if (typeof vgAppicationType != 'undefined' && vgAppicationType == 1 ) {
                    return true;
                }

                var s = w.$FacebookLoader;

                if ('object' !== typeof s.opts) {
                    if ($("#divFacebookLoader").length > 0 && $("#divGoogleLoader").length > 0) {
                        $("#divFacebookLoader").closest('.facebook-btn').css("pointer-events", "none");
                        if ($("#aFBSignup").length > 0)
                            $("#aFBSignup").attr("onclick", "javascript:void(0);");
                        if ($("#aFBLogin").length > 0)
                            $("#aFBLogin").attr("onclick", "javascript:void(0);");
                        $("#divFacebookLoader").show();

                        $("#divGoogleLoader").closest('.facebook-btn').css("pointer-events", "none");
                        if ($("#aGoogleSignUp").length > 0)
                            $("#aGoogleSignUp").attr("onclick", "javascript:void(0);");
                        if ($("#aGoogleLogin").length > 0)
                            $("#aGoogleLogin").attr("onclick", "javascript:void(0);");

                        $("#divGoogleLoader").show();
                    }

                    s.opts = {};
                    s.opts.fbapi = 'f3098c51bd02299a80e63e733e129f47';
                    s.opts.fbapp = '55277e94dcc8fe23e546b0fa0aabb28e';
                    s.opts.appID = '161078477238170';
                    s.opts.appNameSpace = 'vagarobooknow';
                    s.opts.channelURL = '/channel.html';
                    for (var k in options) {
                        s.opts[k] = options[k];
                    }

                    s.cbfn = [];

                    s.abort = function () {
                        while (0 < s.cbfn.length) {
                            s.cbfn.shift()(false);
                        }
                    };

                    s.onLoad = function () {
                        if ('undefined' === typeof FBAPP || 'undefined' === typeof FBAPP.funcCheckInit || false == FBAPP.funcCheckInit()) {
                            setTimeout(s.onLoad, 250);
                            return;
                        }
                        while (0 < s.cbfn.length) {
                            s.cbfn.shift()(true);
                        }
                    };

                    var r = new XMLHttpRequest();
                    r.onerror = s.abort;
                    r.onreadystatechange = function () {
                        if (r.readyState == 4 && (r.status == 200 || r.status == 304)) {
                            eval(r.responseText);
                            s.onLoad();
                        }
                    };
                    r.open("GET", '/JS/Facebook/FacebookLoader.js?v=3bb35dd6cc76ffc3cf6988a833787784');
                    r.send();
                }

                if ('function' === typeof callback) {
                    s.cbfn.push(callback);
                    s.onLoad();
                }

                return true;
            };
        }

        if (0 < ''.length) {
            $FacebookLoader();
        }

    }(window, document));


</script>
